            .bio.padding-bottom30
              p My name is Sydney Anh Mai and I am a product designer. If you don’t work in tech and wonder what that means, let’s just say I design human workflows on the web. My passion for workflow optimization, purposeful interactions, and stellar typography has taken me across industries and products — currently, Kickstarter. I believe that good designers understand the material of their design, be it paper, brick, or code.
              p.padding-top18 I was a bored communication major when I took my first web design class  — it changed my life. When I’m not building weird things in my free time, you can find me waddling at the beach, browsing videos of cats, looking up the capital of Kyrgyzstan, or dancing in heels.
  
    mixin ingredients(...items)
      .row
        .col-sm-10.flex.jc-sb
          each item in items
            if item == items[0]
              h5= item
            else if item == items[1] && items.length == 3
              p.desk-only= item
            else
              p= item
      .row
        .col-sm-10
          hr.clear
    
